      "author": "JoMurray (Jo-Anne Murray)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi I can’t find the answer to my query so posting new.<br />\nI’m fairly new to Monday but loving it so far. We are a construction firm and want to copy an email sent via Outlook into the customers file on our board .<br />\nI don’t fully understand the integration options and not sure how to go about it. Any help gratefully received.<br />\nJo</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 121666,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2023-03-28T12:06:23.697Z",
      "author": "TeamEasy (Easy Mondays)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/jomurray\">@JoMurray</a>,</p>\n<p>Welcome to the community! Sounds like you’re looking for the Emails &amp; Activities feature. Open the line item that pertains to your customers file, and add in the feature if you don’t already have it sitting there.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/c/2c6e1be2fde2d0616c6e4b708f12ce55cca8c15f.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/c/2c6e1be2fde2d0616c6e4b708f12ce55cca8c15f_2_359x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"359\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">713×991 42.7 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/7/373ee1f53f31565e4a09d5b6f91f28a9654f09aa.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/7/373ee1f53f31565e4a09d5b6f91f28a9654f09aa_2_690x276.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"276\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1567×629 62.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Then when you’ve installed it, go and use the settings to connect it to your Outlook account:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/c/2c39c05737addfaa5f1cea7cb3b77ea5742ba54f.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/c/2c39c05737addfaa5f1cea7cb3b77ea5742ba54f_2_618x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"618\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">677×547 30.5 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/6/6653ac5b47ea143b1a928133f8f5072f2c26fe18.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/6/6/6653ac5b47ea143b1a928133f8f5072f2c26fe18_2_419x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"419\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">740×882 41.9 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Hope that’s helpful, have a great day!<br />\n<a href=\"mailto:teameasy@easy-mondays.com\">teameasy@easy-mondays.com</a><br />\nEasy Mondays <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
    },
